body_html:
I haven't tried quantization on InceptionResnetV2, so it's possible there's issues we haven't run across with that model. As a workaround, try changing the quantize_nodes transform to:

quantize_nodes(fallback_min=-10, fallback_max=10)

This is likely to produce less accurate end results, but it will be helpful to see if it gets us past the import error.

body:
I haven't tried quantization on InceptionResnetV2, so it's possible there's issues we haven't run across with that model. As a workaround, try changing the quantize_nodes transform to:

```
quantize_nodes(fallback_min=-10, fallback_max=10)
```

This is likely to produce less accurate end results, but it will be helpful to see if it gets us past the import error.
